Guardian of the Water

Edit on GitHub

PreviousMeja's MemoriesNextShirma's Memories

Overview

UnlockClear Meja's Memories (Chapter 3).
LocationLevia Point (Chapter 3).
Title -
Description Normal dungeon with no restrictions.
Floors 30F Bosses 20F, 30F
Change Crystals 0F, 29F Checkpoints 10F, 20F
Max Level - Bring Buddy Yes
Bring In Items Yes Take Out Items Yes
Shops/Duels Yes Den of Monsters Yes
Reapers Yes Bookmark Yes
Unidentified Equipment, Consumables
Rewards 1. Scholar's Memories (10F).
2. Water Apple (29F).
Chocobo's Max SP 4 5.
3. Dungeon added to Mirror of Memory.
4. Can unlock Shirma's Memories.

Monster Table

Monster Colors - Boss
F - means field of view is limited, N means it's a checkpoint floor.
S - means a Shop Trap can appear.
D - means a Duel Trap can appear.
M - means a Den of Monsters can appear.
R - means Reaper can spawn.
